[More details on the laboratory investigation, allegedly carried out by
IVRI, may help in understanding the etiology and epidemiology of this, so
far obscure, "severe form of gastroenteritis" in simians. Such an
investigation should rule out possible hemorrhagic disease.
Thanks to Pablo Nart for sending a similar item. - Mod.AS]
